{"tid":1417694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正如大師兄講，唔好俾仇恨支配自己。","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:50:37.000Z","uid":101623,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbf76deaf41e4d372469d4d3a2b9bb50159b63c","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"真心，放核彈都唔割。<br />\n但係，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我希望大家唔好再隨便對路人動武。</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔係擔心民意乜乜乜俾藍絲有把柄乜乜乜。<br />\n而係返返去道德既根本，武力本身就係有錯，但只係因為我地除左武力根本冇其他方法同籌碼，我地先要走上勇武之路。<br />\n<br />\n但咁並唔代表我地要向所有人相反立場既人都用到武力，有時真係見到啲人行埋黎屌兩句老母，就個個上晒頭，輕則口角，繼而動武。咁我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知條友單拖走入黎屌人係好on9，但如果我地覺得啲人on9同自己立場唔同就=抵打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁我地同啲廢老藍絲又有乜分別</span><br />\n<br />\n係，佢郁手先唔係唔俾你去反擊保護自己，<br />\n我仲好支持tim⋯⋯<br />\n但唔係一唔岩聽就主動打人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（一手見過）<br />\n明顯我地自己都對唔同立場既人包容度越黎越低<br />\n最慘係仲要人話打得好，<br />\n就係exac7ly平時睇oncc見到啲垃圾留既cm<br />\n我地唔可以令自己變成自己討厭個種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQuote返大師兄一席話<br />\n<br />\n// 但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<br />\n我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？ //<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">共勉之<br />\n不割𥱊<br />\n不篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"b40339d848f998d81e348a8efbd189f788af65fe","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:07:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e1ac079eb42b47e8b01e5bdf374ec4a0de81c16b","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a84d46b1aac76cb260e5814aab8564a9c7642d83","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:09:05.000Z","msg":"Posh"},{"pid":"9b407278424b05be2d7c6bba5e762d828b1d965c","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"Pash"},{"pid":"7bfded3f93b74674170eab5b8054c0f0e9adaae4","tid":1417694,"uid":104035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"盡量保持理性, 但事實好多時班藍絲講兩句就已經想郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26935a351cc13c637a00d93f363f7d9e4ca690a","tid":1417694,"uid":157891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a9d40ab4a60dbebed39adb93844e548d1bbb02b","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7bfded3f93b74674170eab5b8054c0f0e9adaae4","tid":1417694,"uid":104035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"盡量保持理性, 但事實好多時班藍絲講兩句就已經想郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"其實真係理解，<br />\n盡量啦<br />\n真係明個個moment個個激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但！<br />\n呢種行為絕對唔應該鼓吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己人有做得唔夠好既地方都要自省<br />\n唔係我地就會變速龍變藍絲"},{"pid":"82659d4128a12de33e8821b331eb0711cad975cc","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"Pesh"},{"pid":"9aed8157363b8fe09b187252b26741341d021124","tid":1417694,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c86935e77a7ba70411d3cef5cc45916bfe3add5","tid":1417694,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a74e50406b3dbeb69dc95204d8ca54162d5909eb","tid":1417694,"uid